---
import DemoStatsPanel from './demo/DemoStatsPanel.tsx';
---

<section id="demo" class="section bg-white" aria-labelledby="demo-h2">
  <div class="container-content">
    <div class="max-w-3xl" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></span>
        한 번 해보세요
      </span>
      <h2
        id="demo-h2"
        class="mt-6 text-balance text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.12] tracking-tight text-ink md:text-display-lg lg:text-display-xl"
      >
        실제 앱 학습 흐름을<br />
        미리 체험해 보세요.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-prose text-body-lg text-sub text-pretty">
        카드를 넘기며 단어를 익혀보세요. 오른쪽 패널이 진행 상황과 단어별 단계 진화를 실시간 반영합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14" data-reveal>
      <DemoStatsPanel client:visible />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
